    <item>
      <title>I had the immense joy and honor of working with sound collective @densorteskole ...</title>
      <link>https://www.instagram.com/p/DA-fl_jMeXY/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/657367254_18084839579199693_4399573374313124720_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=111&amp;ig_cache_key=MzQ3NjM1NDkwNDU4ODU4NTkxMA%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjk3Mng2NDguc2RyLkMzIn0%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=hAGo6Ck178cQ7kNvwEio2m7&amp;_nc_oc=AdqvZewG99XjwwA6JiAT1B6SenT4NFq8TvDGFoXCCV_5kTHkKFYv0EOYQI5vPsUqQCk&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;se=8&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=OYORz9ebRusb1XCpYCW2Dw&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfxT-tpRmiZK-ZJXwwiwgvw5QzDWtJXw2i5hw_R7F_HjgQ&amp;oe=69C9B1B3" alt="Instagram billede fra @spogelsesmaskinen" /></p><p><strong>@spogelsesmaskinen</strong></p><p>I had the immense joy and honor of working with sound collective @densorteskole and curator @majken_overgaard on creating a new sound and light installation in Christiansborg Palace Church @christiansborgslot in Copenhagen.<br/>
<br/>
I have hand-build 10 glass and steel lanterns to experience during “The blue hour” in the church. The installation is open until 11/12 2024. Opening hours at @christiansborgslot <br/>
<br/>
Majken Overgaard writes:<br/>
The blue hour describes the time of day when the sun sets and twilight descends. The center of the sun is below the horizon, and the blue wavelengths of light color the sky. Day fades, and night is on its way. Throughout history, people have marked this transition, gathered for the twilight hour, and allowed for a slower pace. Now, we mark The Blue Hour in Christiansborg Palace - The Chapel, creating a space for reflection with a new sound and light installation by Den Sorte Skole and Spøgelsesmaskinen.<br/>
<br/>
Photos by @laerkeful 🩵👏</p>]]></description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/657367254_18084839579199693_4399573374313124720_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=111&amp;ig_cache_key=MzQ3NjM1NDkwNDU4ODU4NTkxMA%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjk3Mng2NDguc2RyLkMzIn0%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=hAGo6Ck178cQ7kNvwEio2m7&amp;_nc_oc=AdqvZewG99XjwwA6JiAT1B6SenT4NFq8TvDGFoXCCV_5kTHkKFYv0EOYQI5vPsUqQCk&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;se=8&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=OYORz9ebRusb1XCpYCW2Dw&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfxT-tpRmiZK-ZJXwwiwgvw5QzDWtJXw2i5hw_R7F_HjgQ&amp;oe=69C9B1B3" alt="Instagram billede fra @spogelsesmaskinen" /></p><p><strong>@spogelsesmaskinen</strong></p><p>I had the immense joy and honor of working with sound collective @densorteskole and curator @majken_overgaard on creating a new sound and light installation in Christiansborg Palace Church @christiansborgslot in Copenhagen.<br/>
<br/>
I have hand-build 10 glass and steel lanterns to experience during “The blue hour” in the church. The installation is open until 11/12 2024. Opening hours at @christiansborgslot <br/>
<br/>
Majken Overgaard writes:<br/>
The blue hour describes the time of day when the sun sets and twilight descends. The center of the sun is below the horizon, and the blue wavelengths of light color the sky. Day fades, and night is on its way. Throughout history, people have marked this transition, gathered for the twilight hour, and allowed for a slower pace. Now, we mark The Blue Hour in Christiansborg Palace - The Chapel, creating a space for reflection with a new sound and light installation by Den Sorte Skole and Spøgelsesmaskinen.<br/>
<br/>
Photos by @laerkeful 🩵👏</p>]]></content:encoded>
